## 📋 Phase 6: Implementation Commands

### 6.1 Container Testing Commands
**Daily Container Validation Workflow**:

```bash
# Phase 1: Infrastructure Health Check
elixir scripts/testing/container_health_validator.exs --comprehensive

# Phase 2: Service Integration Validation
elixir scripts/testing/container_integration_tester.exs --all-services

# Phase 3: Demo Execution Testing
elixir scripts/testing/demo_execution_validator.exs --enterprise-scenarios

# Phase 4: Performance Validation
elixir scripts/testing/container_performance_validator.exs --baseline

# Phase 5: Recovery Testing
elixir scripts/testing/container_recovery_tester.exs --failure-scenarios
```

### 6.2 Container Demo Execution Commands
**Systematic Demo Testing Workflow**:

```bash
# Quick Demo Validation (5 minutes)
mix demo --quick --validate --container-health

# Comprehensive Demo Testing (15 minutes)  
mix demo --comprehensive --monitor --performance-tracking

# Container Infrastructure Testing
mix demo --containers-only --health-checks --integration-tests

# Enterprise Scenario Validation
mix demo --enterprise --multi-tenant --real-time --performance
```

### 6.3 Container Management Commands
**Infrastructure Operations**:

```bash
# Container Infrastructure Setup
podman-compose up -d --health-check

# Container Health Monitoring
podman stats --format "table {{.Container}}\t{{.CPUPerc}}\t{{.MemUsage}}\t{{.Status}}"

# Container Log Analysis
podman logs --tail 100 --follow intelitor-app-demo

# Container Cleanup and Reset
podman-compose down --volumes && podman system prune -f
```

